**HW Course chatbot**

1. Firstly make sure you have python version of 3.9.0
2. Make sure you have internet connection, Then you can install all the dependencies using "pip install -r requirements.txt" 
3. Then you can start the chatbot using "streamlit run main.py" command
4. You can switch between different responses using the following keywords as inputs
    (i)   "/sys1" = Information only
    (ii)  "/sys2" = Information with Sources
    (iii) "/sys3" = Sources only
5. You can end the conversation and move to the evaluation using the "/end" command in the user input